00:00:42.544 --> 00:00:44.144 position:24% line:83% align:start
[narrator] This is
 <i>the last opportunity</i>

00:00:44.177 --> 00:00:46.514 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>for Tsubasa and Nankatsu.</i>

00:00:46.548 --> 00:00:47.414 position:19% line:89% align:start
