about this coach?

00:00:53.287 --> 00:00:54.388 position:19% line:89% align:start
You're forgetting that

00:00:54.421 --> 00:00:56.423 position:13% line:83% align:start
this is Taro's last match
with us.

00:00:56.456 --> 00:00:58.425 position:21% line:83% align:start
