schools after.

00:00:58.458 --> 00:01:00.028 position:24% line:83% align:start
We can't deny him
this chance.

00:01:00.060 --> 00:01:01.328 position:41% line:83% align:start
Uh...
Yeah, it's just that...

00:01:01.361 --> 00:01:03.598 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Shiroyama] This moment
means everything

00:01:03.631 --> 00:01:05.533 position:13% line:89% align:start
