00:01:10.838 --> 00:01:12.540 position:24% line:83% align:start
leaving everything
on the pitch.

00:01:12.574 --> 00:01:15.075 position:13% line:83% align:start
Cheer up, we have to pass
the ball to the captain

00:01:15.108 --> 00:01:16.778 position:16% line:83% align:start
no matter what happens.
Here.

00:01:17.812 --> 00:01:21.649 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:01:21.683 --> 00:01:22.382 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Takeshi]
Taro!

00:01:22.416 --> 00:01:24.384 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:01:24.418 --> 00:01:25.653 position:35% line:89% align:start
My son...

00:01:25.687 --> 00:01:27.287 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>Incredible...</i>

00:01:27.321 --> 00:01:29.624 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>He's injured just like me...</i>

00:01:29.657 --> 00:01:30.925 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>and despite that,</i>

00:01:30.959 --> 00:01:33.695 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>he wants to keep playing</i>
 <i>'till the end.</i>

00:01:33.728 --> 00:01:34.796 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Thank you, Taro.</i>

00:01:34.829 --> 00:01:36.030 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>I won't give up either.</i>

00:01:36.064 --> 00:01:37.197 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>I promise you.</i>

00:01:37.230 --> 00:01:38.566 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm going to score</i>
 <i>that goal!</i>

