 <i>at full speed.</i>

00:05:12.814 --> 00:05:14.215 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>We'll see if</i>
 <i>Nankatsu's captain</i>

00:05:14.248 --> 00:05:17.251 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>can score on</i>
 <i>Meiwa's goalkeeper.</i>

00:05:17.285 --> 00:05:18.485 position:24% line:83% align:start
