 <i>to stop him,</i>

00:05:18.519 --> 00:05:20.521 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa runs straight</i>
 <i>towards the goalie,</i>

00:05:20.555 --> 00:05:22.223 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Ken Wakashimazu,</i>
 <i>from Team Meiwa.</i>

00:05:22.256 --> 00:05:24.559 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Ken] <i>Damn it all.</i>
 <i>I have to stop him</i>

00:05:24.592 --> 00:05:26.694 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>or the captain</i>
 <i>won't forgive me.</i>

00:05:26.727 --> 00:05:28.495 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>No matter what</i>
 <i>I have to do...</i>

00:05:28.529 --> 00:05:30.832 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'll stop any shot.</i>

00:05:30.865 --> 00:05:32.300 position:21% line:89% align:start
Keep going, Tsubasa!

00:05:32.332 --> 00:05:34.969 position:16% line:89% align:start
You can do it, Nankatsu!

00:05:35.002 --> 00:05:36.137 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:05:36.170 --> 00:05:37.004 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's hurting.</i>

00:05:37.337 --> 00:05:38.773 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>But...</i>

00:05:38.806 --> 00:05:41.542 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Genzo and Taro worked hard</i>
 <i>to give me this opportunity.</i>

00:05:41.576 --> 00:05:43.778 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>And I won't throw it away.</i>

00:05:43.811 --> 00:05:45.112 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Takeshi]
 <i>I won't let you through!</i>

00:05:45.146 --> 00:05:47.148 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I won't let you shoot,</i>
 <i>Tsubasa!</i>

00:05:47.181 --> 00:05:48.783 position:21% line:83% align:start
